origin.origDate:
Versoris's text was copied 1459; in 1495, in
                        Třeboň, Crux added an index of the QsMeta (ff. 303r–304v), as evident by
                        the colophons: QsMeta book I, f. 11v; book III, f. 30v; book VI, f. 74r;
                        book VII, f. 86r; book X, f. 104r; book XI, f. 109v; book XII, f. 128v;
                        table of contents, f. 304v.

1456–1458, as evident from the colophons:
                        QsPre, f. 70v; QsSex, f. 80r; Qdint book I, f. 108v; QsApri, f. 143v;
                        QsTop, f. 212r.
